@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="about-content">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Welcome to EmpowerHer Health, your trusted destination for women's health excellence. 
        We are committed to providing empathetic care and nurturing a community that uplifts and empowers women to take control of their well-being.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>
        At EmpowerHer Health, our mission is to transform the lives of women by delivering outstanding, personalized healthcare services rooted in compassion, integrity, and empowerment.
        We aim to create a safe, supportive, and inclusive environment where every woman feels seen, heard, and confident in taking charge of her health and well-being.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Team</h3>
    <p>
        Our team of expert healthcare providers, led by dedicated and highly skilled practitioners, offers specialized care in women's health.
        Supported by a caring team of nurses and staff, we are united in our passion for delivering personalized,
        compassionate care that addresses the unique needs and concerns of each woman.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Expertise</h3>
    <p>
        With specialized expertise in women's health,
        our providers work together to deliver comprehensive care that addresses the unique needs of women across all stages of life.
        Our collaborative approach enables us to offer holistic healthcare solutions that integrate physical,
        emotional, and mental well-being, supporting both immediate health concerns and long-term wellness goals.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Values</h3>
    <p>At EmpowerHER Health Group, we embody the following core values:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Compassion</li>
        <li>Integrity</li>
        <li>Excellence</li>
        <li>Community Engagement</li>
        <li>Respect for All</li>
        <li>Collaboration</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
    <p>
        We are dedicated to fostering a safe, inclusive, and empowering environment where every woman feels valued, respected, and supported in her unique health journey.
        Our team is passionate about building strong, lasting relationships with our patients,
        providing a caring and non-judgmental space for women to take control of their health and wellness.
    </p>

    <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
    <p>
        At EmpowerHer Health, we're committed to making a positive impact in our community. We proudly host women's health workshops, provide free health screenings,
        and participate in local events to promote education, empowerment, and proactive wellness. 
        By giving back, we aim to foster a healthier, more informed community that supports the well-being of women and girls.
    </p>

    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
    <p class="contact-info">
        If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our services, please don’t hesitate to contact us.
        We look forward to welcoming you into the EmpowerHER Health Group family!
    </p>
</div>
<br />

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #FDF6F9; 
        color: #4A4A4A; 
